设备</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E4%B8%AD%E7%BB%A7%E5%99%A8%EF%BC%88RP-repeater%EF%BC%89"><span class="nav-number">1.9.2.7.</span> <span class="nav-text">中继器（RP repeater）</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E9%9B%86%E7%BA%BF%E5%99%A8%EF%BC%88Hub%EF%BC%89"><span class="nav-number">1.9.2.8.</span> <span class="nav-text">集线器（Hub）</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E9%93%BE%E8%B7%AF%E5%B1%82%EF%BC%88Data-Link-Layer%EF%BC%89"><span class="nav-number">1.10.</span> <span class="nav-text">数据链路层（Data Link Layer）</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5"><span class="nav-number">1.10.0.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">基本概念</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E5%B0%81%E8%A3%85%E6%88%90%E5%B8%A7%E4%B8%8E%E9%80%8F%E6%98%8E%E4%BC%A0%E8%BE%93"><span class="nav-number">1.10.0.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">封装成帧与透明传输</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E9%80%8F%E6%98%8E%E4%BC%A0%E8%BE%93%E7%9A%84%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8"><span class="nav-number">1.10.0.3.</span> <span class="nav-text">透明传输的应用</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-5"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E8%AE%A1%E6%95%B0%E6%B3%95"><span class="nav-number">1.10.0.3.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">字符计数法</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-5"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E5%A1%AB%E5%85%85%E6%B3%95"><span class="nav-number">1.10.0.3.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">字符填充法</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-5"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E9%9B%B6%E6%AF%94%E7%89%B9%E5%A1%AB%E5%85%85%E6%B3%95"><span class="nav-number">1.10.0.3.3.</span> <span class="nav-text">零比特填充法</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-5"><a class="nav-link" 