 class="nav-link" href="#%E5%90%8E%E9%80%80N%E5%B8%A7%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE%EF%BC%88GBN%EF%BC%89"><span class="nav-number">1.10.0.7.4.</span> <span class="nav-text">后退N帧协议（GBN）</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%B1%82-1"><span class="nav-number">1.11.</span> <span class="nav-text">网络层</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%B1%82%E6%A6%82%E8%BF%B0"><span class="nav-number">1.11.0.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">网络层概述</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#IP%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%80"><span class="nav-number">1.11.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">IP地址</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87"><span class="nav-number">1.11.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">网络设备</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%B1%E5%99%A8"><span class="nav-number">1.11.2.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">路由器</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%B1%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE"><span class="nav-number">1.11.3.</span> <span class="nav-text">路由选择协议</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E4%B8%93%E7%94%A8%E7%BD%91%E5%92%8C%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%80%E8%BD%AC%E6%8D%A2"><span class="nav-number">1.11.3.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">虚拟专用网和网络地址转换</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E4%B8%93%E7%94%A8%E7%BD%91VPN"><span class="nav-number">1.11.3.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">虚拟专用网VPN</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%80%E8%BD%AC%E6%8D%A2NAT"><span class="nav-number">1.11.3.3.</span> <span class="nav-text">网络地址转换NAT</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#IPv6"><span class="nav-number">1.11.3.4.</span> <span class="nav-text">IPv6</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#ICMP"><span class="nav-number">1.11.3.5.</span> <span class="nav-text">ICMP</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#ARP%E5%92%8CRARP"><span class="nav-number">1.11.3.6.</span> <span class="nav-text">ARP和RARP</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E5%B1%82-1"><span class="nav-number">1.12.</span> <span class="nav-text">应用层</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9FDNS"><span class="nav-number">1.12.0.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">域名系统DNS</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E6%A6%82%E8%BF%B0"><span class="nav-number">1.12.0.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">概述</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-5"><a class="nav-link" href="#DNS%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB"><span class="nav-number">1.12.0.2.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">DNS服务器分类</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-5"><a class="nav-link" href="#DNS%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA"><span class="nav-number">1.12.0.2.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">DNS服务器搭建</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#DNS%E6%9F%A5%E8%AF%A2%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B"><span class="nav-number">1.12.0.3.</span> <span class="nav-text">DNS查询流程</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-5"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8%E5%9C%A8%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86IP%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E6%8A%A5%E6%97%B6%E8%A6%81%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8IP%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%80%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%8D%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D%E5%91%A2%EF%BC%9F"><