m nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2"><span class="nav-number">1.12.2.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">历史</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E6%A6%82%E8%BF%B0-1"><span class="nav-number">1.12.2.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">概述</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E7%AE%80%E5%8D%95%E9%82%AE%E4%BB%B6%E4%BC%A0%E9%80%81%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AESMTP"><span class="nav-number">1.12.2.3.</span> <span class="nav-text">简单邮件传送协议SMTP</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E9%82%AE%E4%BB%B6%E8%AF%BB%E5%8F%96%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AEPOP3%E5%92%8C%E7%BD%91%E9%99%85%E6%8A%A5%E6%96%87%E5%AD%98%E5%8F%96%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AEIMAP"><span class="nav-number">1.12.2.4.</span> <span class="nav-text">邮件读取协议POP3和网际报文存取协议IMAP</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E%E4%B8%87%E7%BB%B4%E7%BD%91%E7%9A%84%E7%94%B5%E5%AD%90%E9%82%AE%E4%BB%B6"><span class="nav-number">1.12.2.5.</span> <span class="nav-text">基于万维网的电子邮件</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E9%80%9A%E7%94%A8%E5%9B%A0%E7%89%B9%E7%BD%91%E9%82%AE%E4%BB%B6%E6%89%A9%E5%85%85MIME"><span class="nav-number">1.12.2.6.</span> <span class="nav-text">通用因特网邮件扩充MIME</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-5"><a class="nav-link" href="#MIME%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B%E9%82%AE%E4%BB%B6%E5%A6%82%E4%B8%8B%EF%BC%9A"><span class="nav-number">1.12.2.6.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">MIME示例邮件如下：</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li></ol></li></ol></li></ol></div>
